x2019;s Home Assistant Will Soon Be Getting a Sense of Smell</h1>\n<p><strong>Your smart assistant will soon be even smarter as Google unveil a new and improved version of their Google Home assistant.</strong></p>\n<figure style=\"max-width: 1600px;\"><div style=\"padding-top: 66.6875%; background-color: rgba(201,196,188, 0.5);\"><img src=\"/images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-800.jpg\" alt=\"Google Home in kitchen\" srcset=\"/images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-100.jpg 100w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-200.jpg 200w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-300.jpg 300w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-400.jpg 400w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-500.jpg 500w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-600.jpg 600w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-700.jpg 700w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-800.jpg 800w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-900.jpg 900w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-1000.jpg 1000w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-1100.jpg 1100w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-1200.jpg 1200w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-1300.jpg 1300w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-1400.jpg 1400w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-1500.jpg 1500w, /images/google-home-sense-of-smell-b3cbb83155dc9fb501b099f3546f3ee102ff65550b08a1edd6aeaa6f738a6e51-1600.jpg 1600w\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" style class=\"fadeInOnLoad\" loading=\"eager\"></div><figcaption>Photograph: Jonas Leupe <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@jonasleupe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@jonasleupe</a></figcaption></figure>\n<p>Bob tiersy, director of Google hardware said in a statement that &#xAB;In an effort to harvest as much data as we can from our users, the next logical thing to do was to not just be able to hear and see what&#x2019;s going on in people&#x2019;s home but also be able to smell&#xBB;.</p>\n<p>This new update will allow Google to target people based on their dietary habits, hygiene levels, pets, cigarette smoke. For exemple, it might suggest you a new brand of perfume if you happen to stink. Remind you to empty your cat litter box or create reminders to Take out the trash.</p>\n<p>This new capability is made possible by their newly developed olfactory sensor.</p>\n<p>Devices released after may 2015 are already equipped with this capability. An over the air update will soon be released to enable the feature. The company says it will pay customers with older devices to receive the upgrade.</p>\n</body></html>","readingTime":"1 min read","absoluteUrl":"https://therelease.news/article/google-home-sense-of-smell","timestamp":1444734780000,"keywords":"Tag, Another Tag"},"nextArticles":[]},"__N_SSG":true}